Raised By Ghosts  Dr. Strange and I Wanna Be Your Dog Live at Mojo Main

The two closing songs of the Wilmington DE band Raised By Ghosts live set performed at Mojo Main in Newark DE on 62513. Both songs now featuring More Jackson Dr. Strange is an original song followed by a cover of The Stooges classic. Sorry about the crotch shot between songs but I forgot to turn the camera off.
